I ate the day before.

48:51.303 --> 48:53.346
Counting every calorie
so l know exactly...

48:53.514 --> 48:56.474
...how much self-loathing
to take into the shower.

48:56.851 --> 48:58.518
I'm going for it.

48:58.686 --> 49:02.022
I have no interest in being obese.
