watch the soccer game.

49:08.154 --> 49:10.572
And tomorrow we're gonna go
on a little date...

49:10.740 --> 49:14.159
...and buy ourselves
some bigger jeans.

49:15.369 --> 49:17.829
Giovanni likes a muffin.

49:21.042 --> 49:22.208
Attagirl.

49:36.557 --> 49:38.892
He's saying,
