when you're 1 0...

01:59:31.623 --> 01:59:33.791
...and having your father
kiss you on the mouth.

01:59:33.959 --> 01:59:35.542
He still does it.

01:59:35.710 --> 01:59:39.421
I'm sure it's all normal in Brazil,
but I didn't grow up in Brazil.

01:59:39.589 --> 01:59:41.382
Friends would tease
the crap out of me.

01:59:41.549 --> 01:59:43.050
Why didn't you ask him to stop?

01:59:43.218 --> 01:59:45.678
No, I did at first,
but then l realized...

01:59:45.845 --> 01:59:48.639
...how happy it made the old guy
and l just gave in.

01:59:48.807 --> 01:59:53.602
You know what? My grandmother
hikes faster than you both...

01:59:53.770 --> 01:59:56.230
...but she's already dead.

01:59:56.398 --> 01:59:59.149
Get him. Go get him.

01:59:59.317 --> 02:00:02.486
How about you carry the packs
for a while, eh?

02:00:02.737 --> 02:00:05.280
Come here. Look at this.

02:00:05.657 --> 02:00:07.574
Is it nice?

02:00:08.118 --> 02:00:09.159
Baby.

02:00:10.161 --> 02:00:12.246
Bringing up the rear.

02:00:22.007 --> 02:00:24.758
-So have you slept with her yet?
-What was that?

02:00:24.926 --> 02:00:26.301
Have you slept with her yet?

02:00:26.469 --> 02:00:28.178
Crossing the line.

02:00:28.346 --> 02:00:32.141
Dad, it's been 1 0 years. lt's time.

02:00:44.612 --> 02:00:46.989
Stay away from
all the beautiful girls.

02:00:47.157 --> 02:00:49.533
They are dangerous.

02:00:54.372 --> 02:00:56.123
-A week is too short.
-Yeah.

02:00:56.291 --> 02:00:59.209
-A week is too short.
-Yup.

02:00:59.794 --> 02:01:03.172
Listen, l've made you a mixtape.

02:01:03.882 --> 02:01:06.383
And l give you a present. For you.

